  <h2>Fixed layout</h2>
  <p>Provides a common fixed-width (and responsive) layout with only <code>&lt;div class="container"&gt;</code> required.</p>
  <div class="mini-layout">
    <div class="mini-layout-body"></div>
  </div>
<div class="tab-content">
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade in active" id="fixed-layout-haml">
%body
  .container
    \...
</pre>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade" id="fixed-layout-html">
&lt;body&gt;
  &lt;div class="container"&gt;
    ...
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
</pre>
</div>
  <ul class="nav nav-pills example-types">
    <li class="active"><a href="#fixed-layout-haml" data-toggle="tab">HAML</a></li>
