  <h2>Fluid layout</h2>
  <p>Create a fluid, two-column page with <code>&lt;div class="container-fluid"&gt;</code>&mdash;great for applications and docs.</p>
  <div class="mini-layout fluid">
    <div class="mini-layout-sidebar"></div>
    <div class="mini-layout-body"></div>
  </div>
<div class="tab-content">
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade in active" id="fluid-layout-haml">
.container-fluid
  .row-fluid
    .span2
      / Sidebar content
    .span10
      / Body content
</pre>
<pre class="prettyprint linenums tab-pane fade" id="fluid-layout-html">
&lt;div class="container-fluid"&gt;
  &lt;div class="row-fluid"&gt;
    &lt;div class="span2"&gt;
      &lt;!--Sidebar content--&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
    &lt;div class="span10"&gt;
      &lt;!--Body content--&gt;
    &lt;/div&gt;
  &lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
</pre>
</div>
